        " سَمِعْتُهُ يَقُولُ : «أَكْرَهُ أَنْ يَنَامَ اَلْمُحْرِمُ عَلَى اَلْفِرَاشِ اَلْأَصْفَرِ أَوِ اَلْمِرْفَقَةِ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2620 - Abu Basir narrated from Abu Ja'far (as), who said:\n\"I dislike for a Muhrim to sleep on a yellow mattress or a yellow cushion.\""
        ]
